  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The big satisfaction when I came to Israel, and I [? saw ?] the Polacks, how they work, and now they're happy to be in Palestine, Israel, and to make money by the Jews.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] and the [NON-ENGLISH], two Jewish papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I read them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I liked-- that time, I liked books.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I read a little bit, but my father used to tell me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to ask him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He liked to discuss with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He liked to discuss.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- he told-- he always told that I-- I have his head, because my brother hate business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't like business terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Yeshiva [NON-ENGLISH] didn't like business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He married a business lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was in the business, and he helped her out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sister married, and my fourth, Mindel, she-- my mother didn't know even what kind of business my father has.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I can explain from the farm, and I can explain from the forest, what from which tree you can make out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to go with my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to take me when I had the vacation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to take girlfriends with me too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to explain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, I ask it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not only explain, I ask it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Daddy, ?] why you make from this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You say this furniture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He'd say furniture needs to be-- should be this, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And for eating, there must be the [INAUDIBLE] for eating the [INAUDIBLE] wood, you know, for fall out, yes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he explained-- explained me, and I know it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I know he showed me how to measure, and how to make the material-- everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I liked this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I come I on the farm, then I look at everything.",
